# Git commits

When creating git commits in this repository:

- Never add `Co-authored-by` trailers (including for Cursor, cursoragent, or any AI assistant).
- Use commit messages authored only as Parrot Playlabs; the repo is configured with `user.name` and `user.email` locally.
- Do not append sign-offs, trailers, or attribution lines beyond the commit subject and body.
